SafeNet AT 
----------

Description
	The SafeNet AT application for Splunk (R) provides a number of security reports and
	enables search operations that can be used to extract information from the log streams
	produced by KeySecure appliances and ProtectFile agents.

	Dashboard panel information is extracted from audit, activity, system, and ProtectFile
	logs.  This requires that the KeySecure appliance be setup to forward logs to Splunk.

	* KeySecure currently only writes plain text entries to syslog.

	* This app handles KeySecure log files formatted according to both RFC3164 and RFC5424.

Version
	1.6 - updated 11 February 2020
